EUROPE
• From Dallas-Fort Worth, the only service to
London's convenient Gatwick Airport, all
747s, everyday, plus the only 747 thru-plane
service to Amsterdam, Brussels and Frankfurt.
• From Boston, Braniff has the only non-stop
747 service to all of these European cities -

close-in Orly Airport.

SOUTH
AMERICA
• From New York's JFK Airport, Braniff offers
the only non-stop service to Panama plus
non stops to Buenos Aires and Guayaquil.
• From Miami, Braniff flies non-stop to Rio de
Janeiro, Buenos Aires, Bogota, Guayaquil,
Lima, Panama and Quito.
• From Los Angeles and San Francisco, Branift
has the only thru service to Sao Paulo,
continuing on to Rio. Plus non-stops to
Bogota, Lima and Santiago from Los Angeles;
thru from San Francisco.
• From New Orleans, Braniff has the only non-
stop service to Maracaibo and Panama and the
only thru service to Caracas.
We better be better.
